    "attributes": {
        "action": "Review of the Council Tax Band system.",
        "additional_details": "According to the Nationwides House Price Index Calculator house Prices have risen 292.65% from 1991 Q1 to 2018 Q4.\r\n\r\nA realistic look and long term plan needs to put in place to amend the bands accordingly as prices increase or an overhaul of the system and a new tax plan needs to take its place as the current one is almost 30 years old and outdated.",
        "background": "In 1991 Council Tax Bands were set from A-H from \u00a30 to over \u00a3320,000.\r\n\r\nThis system is no longer relevant or fit for purpose.",
